Name: Lesser Aett Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Basic Aett Rune, Level 1 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes the words from a noble's mouth, the speech of a leader, the silvertongue of a merchant. It grants those who channel it greater charm and influence.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACECommanding SpeechSPACEAs an action, you give a speech to a creature within DISTANCE30-90DISTANCE feet of you that can hear you. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be charmed by you. While charmed by you in this way, the target must take the Hide action on their turn. The creature may repeat this saving throw at the end of each of their turns, ending this effect on a success.SPACESPACEYou may use this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest.
